Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.73,0:22:09.23,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}INSIDE  IDENTITY
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.23,0:22:12.03,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我的栖身之地在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.16,0:22:24.67,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}误解令人感到害羞什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.75,0:22:27.25,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}率真令人难以忍受什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:29.59,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}无论他人怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.59,0:22:32.47,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我也不知到底「正确」为何物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.51,0:22:35.09,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}强迫自己去习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.30,0:22:37.68,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}一成不变的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:40.43,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}将沉沦的种种个性
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.52,0:22:42.64,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}啃食饮尽  唾弃嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:47.27,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}希望你能理解这样的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:52.61,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}欲言又止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.69,0:22:57.57,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}连思考「为什么谁人都无法理解我」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.70,0:23:02.66,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}都已成为一种奢侈了吗？了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.87,0:23:07.96,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}多愁善感的太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.04,0:23:10.67,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}释放出过多的热量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.75,0:23:13.09,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}把我晒得快不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.21,0:23:18.18,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}按耐不住呐喊的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.34,0:23:24.18,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不顾一切地渴求IDENTITY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.18,0:23:26.64,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}INSIDE  MY  FEELING
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.73,0:23:29.23,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}INSIDE  MY  JUSTICE
